43:54.128 --> 43:58.003
A few days ago,
I was stuck there in the elevator.

43:58.104 --> 43:59.404
Really?

43:59.821 --> 44:03.274
- It must have been frightening.
- Yes, I was so scared.

44:03.617 --> 44:05.416
I'm scared of elevators too.

44:06.001 --> 44:12.056
- You mean, even when they work properly?
- Actually, I hate elevators.

44:13.248 --> 44:15.849
Yes, I see. So let's go walking.

44:15.950 --> 44:17.453
Sure. It's okay.

44:20.602 --> 44:22.136
I like this painting.

44:23.624 --> 44:24.924
They look alright.

44:25.747 --> 44:29.311
- But they're kind of strange, too.
- Oh, you think so?

44:29.784 --> 44:31.084
They are strange.

44:32.079 --> 44:33.379
Don't you think?

44:37.174 --> 44:40.339
Yes, they're strange looking at it now.

44:41.638 --> 44:42.938
Yes.

44:43.039 --> 44:46.333
- Very strange.
- Yes, very strange.

45:04.151 --> 45:06.333
- Eat some fruit.
- Thanks.

45:06.516 --> 45:08.105
It was a great meal.

45:09.174 --> 45:11.270
