46:40.590 --> 46:44.339
- I'm happy you like it.
- Yes, this one is very beautiful.

46:46.091 --> 46:49.441
- You have great talent.
- Oh, thank you very much.

46:54.984 --> 46:56.284
What is it?

46:57.901 --> 46:59.933
