47:40.011 --> 47:41.994
Look, it's Director So.

47:44.270 --> 47:45.939
It's really him.

47:46.873 --> 47:48.253
How funny.

47:49.334 --> 47:51.047
How did she get it?

47:52.971 --> 47:54.399
