48:47.107 --> 48:48.745
Oh, I didn't know that.

48:49.642 --> 48:51.699
She's the one who fired you?

48:51.950 --> 48:54.542
Yes, she did.

48:55.082 --> 48:58.321
- Even without telling me why.
- Really?

48:58.836 --> 49:00.136
Can they do that?

49:00.721 --> 49:02.431
Yes, they can do that.

49:02.996 --> 49:08.111
She told some very strange
reason to dismiss me.

49:09.457 --> 49:10.757
What's it?

