49:19.605 --> 49:22.944
But she didn't tell me why

49:23.045 --> 49:26.007
she thinks I'm dishonest person.

49:27.784 --> 49:30.074
Is she an honest person herself?

49:34.817 --> 49:36.204
I don't think so.

49:43.433 --> 49:46.095
I wonder what she was
thinking when she dismissed you.

49:46.196 --> 49:48.099
You're such a nice girl!

49:49.070 --> 49:51.225
I think I know why now.

49:54.701 --> 49:56.001
Do you?

49:56.701 --> 49:59.213
- What is it?
- I think...

50:02.313 --> 50:03.988
I better tell you later.

50:05.857 --> 50:07.699
She was just jealous.

50:08.048 --> 50:09.348
Yeah?

50:11.513 --> 50:13.841
- She was jealous?
- Yes.

50:16.387 --> 50:17.785
Excuse.

51:22.553 --> 51:25.434
- You want another more?
- Yes, thank you.

51:25.617 --> 51:29.436
The same, please.

51:29.537 --> 51:31.137
- Thank you.
- No problem.

51:42.251 --> 51:44.788
- Manhee, it's you.
- Director?

51:45.261 --> 51:48.304
- Nice to see you.
